  <p> This is a <b>memory game.</b> You shall win by obtaining the <b>highest score</b>. Earn points by <b>correctly matching</b> calls with their content.
You will have <b>10 seconds</b> to memorize the content of each cell.</p>
<img src="s.jpg" alt="First instruction" width="400" height="300">
  <p> After 10 seconds, the cards will <b>flip</b> and a question card will <b>pop up</b>  </p>
  <img src="s2.jpg" alt="Second instruction" width="400" height="300">
  <p>  You will then match the contents of the question card with the corresponding cell.
<b><br><span style="text-align: center; color: purple">Correct match = 500 <span style="color: purple">points</span>.<br> Incorrect match = 0 points.</b>
</p></span>
<p>You can monitor your score evolution on the screen as you play.

